## Current `/api/spider/config` Route Shape

`packages/plugins/spider/src/oculus-routes.ts`:

Returns:
```json
{
  "rigTemplates": { /* only guild.json-declared templates */ },
  "engineDesigns": [ { "id": "...", "pluginId": "...", "hasCollect": false } ],
  "blockTypes": [ { "id": "...", "pluginId": "...", "pollIntervalMs": 60000 } ]
}
```

**Critical gap:** `rigTemplates` comes from `guildConfig().spider.rigTemplates` — only config-declared templates. Kit-contributed templates (registered via `RigTemplateRegistry.registerFromKit()`) are completely absent. The template registry (`rigTemplateRegistry`) lives in spider.ts's closure with no public getter.

