## Current Spider Page Behavior

### `packages/plugins/spider/src/static/index.html`

Two tabs: **Rigs** and **Config**.

**Rigs tab:**
- `#rig-list-view` — toolbar (status filter select, writ-id text filter, date-range inputs, refresh button), `#rig-table` headers: `ID | Writ | Status | Engines | Created`
- `#rig-detail-view` (hidden) — back button, `#detail-title` h2, `#detail-meta` table (inside `.card`), `#pipeline` div, `#engine-detail` card

**Config tab:**
- `#templates-section` — currently rendered as key→JSON blocks (`.template-block` divs with h3 + pre/code)
- `#designs-table` — ID, Plugin, Has Collect
- `#blocktypes-table` — ID, Plugin, Poll Interval

### `packages/plugins/spider/src/static/spider.js` — key functions

**State vars:** `rigs[]`, `currentRig`, `selectedEngineId`, `sortField`, `sortDir`, `configData`, `currentStatusFilter`

**`fetchRigs(statusFilter)`** → `GET /api/rig/list?limit=100[&status=...]`

**`renderRigList()`** → rows: `ID(link) | writId(link) | status(badge) | engineSummary | createdAt`. Client-side sort, writ-id text filter, date range filter.

**`showRigDetail(rig)`** → switches views, populates `#detail-meta` table (ID, Writ link, Status, Created), calls `renderPipeline(rig)`.

**`renderPipeline(rig)`** → topoSorts engines, renders horizontal row of `.pipeline-node` divs with `→` arrows between. Clicking a node calls `showEngineDetail(engine)`.

**`showEngineDetail(engine)`** → DL list: Status, Design ID, Upstream, Started At, Completed At, Error, Session ID, block fields. Collapsibles for Givens Spec and Yields.

**`fetchConfig()`** → `GET /api/spider/config` (lazy on first Config tab visit)

**`renderConfig()`** → templates as key/JSON blocks; designs table; block types table.

